headline.main: Bird Flu Found at Tyson Foods Chicken Supplier
headline.print_headline: Bird Flu Found at Tyson Foods Chicken Supplier

lead_paragraph: Tens of thousands of chickens have been destroyed at a Tennessee chicken farm due to a bird flu outbreak, and 30 other farms within a six-mile radius have been quarantined.
